(hit a wall / crate / hero that ISN'T a mirror: the ray is blocked, no reflection)
[ > Counter | Solid no Mirror ] -> [ | Solid ]

(first mirror hit: bounce, and switch permanently into Returning mode. Mundane only does secondary/tertiary reflections)
left    [ > Counter no Returning | MirrorUR no Mundane ] -> [ | MirrorUR up    Counter Primary   ]
+ left  [ > Counter no Returning | MirrorDR no Mundane ] -> [ | MirrorDR down  Counter Primary   ]
+ right [ > Counter no Returning | MirrorUL no Mundane ] -> [ | MirrorUL up    Counter Primary   ]
+ right [ > Counter no Returning | MirrorDL no Mundane ] -> [ | MirrorDL down  Counter Primary   ]
+ up    [ > Counter no Returning | MirrorDL no Mundane ] -> [ | MirrorDL left  Counter Primary   ]
+ up    [ > Counter no Returning | MirrorDR no Mundane ] -> [ | MirrorDR right Counter Primary   ]
+ down  [ > Counter no Returning | MirrorUL no Mundane ] -> [ | MirrorUL left  Counter Primary   ]
+ down  [ > Counter no Returning | MirrorUR no Mundane ] -> [ | MirrorUR right Counter Primary   ]

(Secondary reflection)
+ left  [ > Counter Primary      | MirrorUR            ] -> [ | MirrorUR up    Counter Secondary ]
+ left  [ > Counter Primary      | MirrorDR            ] -> [ | MirrorDR down  Counter Secondary ]
+ right [ > Counter Primary      | MirrorUL            ] -> [ | MirrorUL up    Counter Secondary ]
+ right [ > Counter Primary      | MirrorDL            ] -> [ | MirrorDL down  Counter Secondary ]
+ up    [ > Counter Primary      | MirrorDL            ] -> [ | MirrorDL left  Counter Secondary ]
+ up    [ > Counter Primary      | MirrorDR            ] -> [ | MirrorDR right Counter Secondary ]
+ down  [ > Counter Primary      | MirrorUL            ] -> [ | MirrorUL left  Counter Secondary ]
+ down  [ > Counter Primary      | MirrorUR            ] -> [ | MirrorUR right Counter Secondary ]

(Tertiary reflection)
+ left  [ > Counter Secondary    | MirrorUR            ] -> [ | MirrorUR up    Counter Tertiary  ]
+ left  [ > Counter Secondary    | MirrorDR            ] -> [ | MirrorDR down  Counter Tertiary  ]
+ right [ > Counter Secondary    | MirrorUL            ] -> [ | MirrorUL up    Counter Tertiary  ]
+ right [ > Counter Secondary    | MirrorDL            ] -> [ | MirrorDL down  Counter Tertiary  ]
+ up    [ > Counter Secondary    | MirrorDL            ] -> [ | MirrorDL left  Counter Tertiary  ]
+ up    [ > Counter Secondary    | MirrorDR            ] -> [ | MirrorDR right Counter Tertiary  ]
+ down  [ > Counter Secondary    | MirrorUL            ] -> [ | MirrorUL left  Counter Tertiary  ]
+ down  [ > Counter Secondary    | MirrorUR            ] -> [ | MirrorUR right Counter Tertiary  ]

(Returning: count back down)
+ [ > 30 Returning | no Solid ] -> [ | > 29 Returning LOS ]
+ [ > 29 Returning | no Solid ] -> [ | > 28 Returning LOS ]
+ [ > 28 Returning | no Solid ] -> [ | > 27 Returning LOS ]
+ [ > 27 Returning | no Solid ] -> [ | > 26 Returning LOS ]
