+ [ > 02 Tertiary  | no Solid ] [ action Reflectable ] -> [ | BaseReflection ] [ Reflectable HasReflection ]
+ [ > 02 Returning | no Solid ] -> [ | > 01 Returning LOS ]

+ [ > 01 Secondary | no Solid ] [ action MirrorGuy ]        -> [ | MirrorGuyReflection ] [ MirrorGuy HasReflection ]
+ [ > 01 Secondary | no Solid ] [ action SMirrorGuy ]       -> [ | MirrorGuyReflection ] [ SMirrorGuy HasReflection ]
+ [ > 01 Secondary | no Solid ] [ action ReflectableCrate ] -> [ | CrateReflection     ] [ ReflectableCrate HasReflection ]
